                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Sub 2
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Sub 3
                        </p>
                    </li>

                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h2>
                    Main 2
                </h2>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    Main 3
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="fancyRight">

        <h2 class="text-center">
            Game General Information
        </h2>

        <p class="frontPageTextFirstLetter">
            War of Rights is a multiplayer game set during the perilous days of the American Civil War,
            in the Maryland Campaign of September, 1862. Campfire Games is devoted to presenting the gruesome
            and glorious elements of the period, while maintaining the highest level of historical
            accuracy and realism as is possible with the wonders of CRYENGINE.
            <br>
        </p>

    </div>



    <div class="fancyClearBoth"></div>

    @await Html.PartialAsync("_CompanyRanking")

</div>